{
  "title": "Laced Peruvian Carrot Stew",
  "description": "A mustardy, crumbly one-pot stew with sautéed carrots, toasted pumpkin seeds, and bright lime, perfect for a paleo-friendly Peruvian lunch or dinner.",
  "cuisine": "Peruvian",
